race.comment: Looks a good race for PHANTOM'S CHASE (3) who is bursting to win. Has placed three of the last four, the latest gave a sight over further at Seymour. Looks a leading chance to land an overdue win. IRISH BLOOM (9) was safely held fresh then improved sharply out in journey last time. Fitter again and extra trip a plus. PLASTIC DREAMS (4) was disappointing last time but ran well the start prior. Has speed and can give a sight on best figures. PLAY IT COOL (8) has raced only twice and was beaten 22 lengths last time when just didn't handle a wet track. Did run very well only other start and back in trip and on firmer ground expecting a huge run.
